Class Product

java.lang.Object
com.madj.Product
@Entity public class Product extends Object

    • Product

      public Product(int id, int price, String title, String desc, String img, Product.ProductType productType)
      Parameterized constructor.
      Parameters:
      id - The product's id. Consistent throughout the local H2 database and Google Cloud database.
      price - The product's price. Should be multiplied by 100 to be stored in an int.
      title - The product's name.
      desc - The product's description.
      img - The product's image url.
      productType - The type of product.
